(17, 'utility companies', 'utility-companies', '', '<div class="container" style="margin-bottom: 50px;">\r\n    <p style="text-transform: uppercase;">Please submit your request and team Homula will follow up for you</p>\r\n    <div>\r\n        <div id="form-utility">\r\n            <div role="form" class="wpcf7" id="wpcf7-f1815-p1254-o1" lang="en-US" dir="ltr">\r\n                <div class="screen-reader-response"></div>\r\n                <form action="/utility-companies/#wpcf7-f1815-p1254-o1" method="post" class="wpcf7-form ng-pristine ng-valid" novalidate="novalidate">\r\n                    <div style="display: none;">\r\n                        <input type="hidden" name="_wpcf7" value="1815">\r\n                        <input type="hidden" name="_wpcf7_version" value="4.5.1">\r\n                        <input type="hidden" name="_wpcf7_locale" value="en_US">\r\n                        <input type="hidden" name="_wpcf7_unit_tag" value="wpcf7-f1815-p1254-o1">\r\n                        <input type="hidden" name="_wpnonce" value="021e5efa08">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="cformfield">\r\n                        <div class="wrap-shadow"><span> Your Name (required)</span><span class="wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-name"><input type="text" name="your-name" value="" size="40" class="wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-text wpcf7-validates-as-required" aria-required="true" aria-invalid="false"></span> </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="cformfield">\r\n                        <div class="wrap-shadow"> <span>Your Email (required)</span> <span class="wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-email"><input type="email" name="your-email" value="" size="40" class="wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-text wpcf7-email wpcf7-validates-as-required wpcf7-validates-as-email" aria-required="true" aria-invalid="false"></span> </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="cformfield">\r\n                        <div class="wrap-shadow"> <span>Request (required)</span> <span class="wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-request"><textarea name="your-request" cols="40" rows="10" class="wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-textarea wpcf7-validates-as-required" aria-required="true" aria-invalid="false" style="overflow: hidden; word-wrap: break-word; height: 98px;"></textarea></span> </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="cformbtn">\r\n                        <input type="submit" value="Submit" class="wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-submit"><img class="ajax-loader" src="http://realestate.homula.com/wp-content/plugins/contact-form-7/images/ajax-loader.gif" alt="Sending ..." style="visibility: hidden;"></div>\r\n                    <div class="wpcf7-response-output wpcf7-display-none"></div>\r\n                </form>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="effect-1">\r\n            <div style="background: #fff;padding: 25px;border: 1px solid #dcdcdc;">\r\n                <div id="phone-list"><strong>Embridge:</strong><br>Call 1-866-763-5427\r\n                    <hr /> <strong> Power Stream:</strong><br>Call 1-877-963-6900\r\n                    <hr /> <strong> Toronto hydro:</strong><br>Call: (416) 542-8000\r\n                    <hr /> <strong> Reliance:</strong><br>Call 1-888-837-1451</div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="content-1">\r\n    <div class="container" style="padding-top: 40px;">\r\n	    <p>At Homula, our Toronto <a href="http://realestate.homula.com/agents/">real estate experts</a> work hard to ensure you have the ability to lay back and enjoy your new home. As such, we communicate with some of the major utilities companies prior to you settling in so that your monthly costs are laid out and simple to understand. Our experts pair you with the utility plan and <a href="http://realestate.homula.com/mls-listing/">MLS listing</a> of your dreams.</p>\r\n	    <p><a href="http://realestate.homula.com/faq/">With our help</a>, you do not have to worry about calling company to company in hopes of finding the best deal. Based on your needs, we will make the calls and find you a deal that will be undeniably perfect. Our professionals are devoted, diligent and extremely trustworthy. You can count on our knowledge.</p>\r\n	    <p>We are ready to connect you with the following world renowned utility companies</p>\r\n        <div class="utility_tab-pane">\r\n            <ul class="nav nav-tabs">\r\n                <li class="active"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#home1">Enbridge:</a></li>\r\n                <li><a data-toggle="tab" href="#menu11">PowerStream Energy Services:</a></li>\r\n                <li><a data-toggle="tab" href="#menu22">Reliance:</a></li>\r\n                <li><a data-toggle="tab" href="#menu33">Toronto hydro:</a></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <div class="tab-content">\r\n                <div class="tab-pane fade in active" id="home1">\r\n                    <div class="wrap-tab-pane-content">\r\n                    	<p>For over 65 years, Enbridge has been effectively delivering energy in North America. Their dedication, hard work and proven techniques has enabled them to be recognized as one of the Global 100 Most Sustainable Corporation in the world. Safety is the number one priority of this excellent energy company. Enbridge has had a 99.9994% safe delivery record through their crude oil pipelines for the past 10 years!</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="menu11">\r\n                    <div class="wrap-tab-pane-content">\r\n                    	<p>A subsidiary of PowerStream Holdings Inc., PowerStream Energy Services was established in 2013. This electricity distribution company, owned by the city of Markham, Vaughan and Barrie, provides Sub-Metering services to both commercial properties and condos throughout Canada! PowerStream Energy Services works closely with our experts at Homula in order to exceed your needs. From commissioning to installation, you can count on the experienced technicians at PowerStream Energy Services.</p>\r\n	                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="menu22">\r\n                    <div class="wrap-tab-pane-content">\r\n                    	<p>Incorporated in 1929, Reliance Infrastructure companies distribute over 36 billion units of energy to over 30 million consumers. Reliance is one of the most trusted utility companies in the world today. With their vow to continuously offer 24/7 phone support, they have truly become one of the leaders in the industry.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="menu33">\r\n                    <div class="wrap-tab-pane-content">\r\n                    	<p>The largest municipal electricity distribution company, Toronto Hydro, currently distributes 18% of the electricity consumed in Ontario. This zealous energy company also services around 740,000 customers in Toronto!<p>\r\n                    	<p>At Homula, our Toronto real estate experts work hard to ensure you have the ability to lay back and enjoy your new home. As such, we communicate with some of the major utilities companies prior to you settling in so that your monthly costs are laid out and simple to understand. Our experts pair you with the utility plan and MLS listing of your dreams.</p>\r\n                    	<p>With our help, you do not have to worry about calling company to company in hopes of finding the best deal. Based on your needs, we will make the calls and find you a deal that will be undeniably perfect. Our professionals are devoted, diligent and extremely trustworthy. You can count on our knowledge.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="content-2">\r\n    <div class="container">\r\n    	<p><strong class="choosing">Choosing the Right Supplier</strong></p> \r\n    	<p>All of the utility companies that we&rsquo;ve listed above are guaranteed to provide quality service, but how do you know which one is the best choice for you? Our Toronto real estate experts outline some suggestions below that can help you get started on the path towards finding the ideal utility company for your needs.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container utility_tab-pane">\r\n    <ul class="nav nav-tabs">\r\n        <li class="active"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#home">Spending Costs:</a></li>\r\n        <li><a data-toggle="tab" href="#menu1">Pricing Plans:</a></li>\r\n        <li><a data-toggle="tab" href="#menu2">Do Your Research:</a></li>\r\n        <li><a data-toggle="tab" href="#menu3">Taxes, Charges and Fees:</a></li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n    <div class="tab-content">\r\n        <div class="tab-pane fade in active" id="home">\r\n            <div class="wrap-tab-pane-content">\r\n            	<p>Before you make any commitments, take a look at what you&rsquo;ve been spending on utilities using recent statements from your current supplier and pinpoint a price range that you think sounds reasonable. After this, you can compare your spending costs to the current plans available through the companies above and narrow down the ones that suit your energy usage and price range the best.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="menu1">\r\n            <div class="wrap-tab-pane-content">\r\n            	<p>Competitive energy companies typically offer two types of pricing contracts: fixed and variable prices. Fixed price contracts offer the same rate for energy throughout your contract term, meaning you will have more protection against shifting energy prices. Alternatively, variable prices &ndash; also referred to as floating prices &ndash; are based on the wholesale market price for energy and include an additional surcharge. These plans are best for periods when energy prices are low, but run the risk of higher prices when price spikes occur. Do your research into the energy market and determine the plan that is best for you. In general, fixed price contracts are ideal if you&rsquo;re planning a contract of at least two months in order to ensure maximum savings.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="menu2">\r\n            <div class="wrap-tab-pane-content">\r\n            	<p>Take a close look at each plan and determine the savings that will be gained from each one. In addition, consider the terms and conditions of each plan that you are considering and make sure that you&rsquo;re fully aware of the commitments that you will be bound to upon enlisting the services of the company. The last thing that you want is to enter into a contract that contains terms that you overlooked, which can cause numerous headaches and extra fees down the road.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="menu3">\r\n            <div class="wrap-tab-pane-content">\r\n            	<p>Speaking of fees, make sure to ask yourself this: Do the prices listed include any taxes, charges or fees? Each of the companies above can provide you with a clear look at the kind of additional charges that you can expect, so compare and contrast each one and determine the plans that are worth the fees for you and the plans that aren&rsquo;t. Keep an eye out for early exit fees, which are charged by certain competitive price energy contracts, as well as late payment fees and failed payment charges. Most energy suppliers have different late fee policies, so definitely make sure that you understand the differences between each one.</p>\r\n            	<p>Finding the right utility company will help you keep your costs low and allow you to enjoy your new home with a sense of security. As you can see from the tips above, there are many options at your fingertips, each one more suitable to different people depending on their unique situation.</p>\r\n            	</p><strong><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/agents/" target="_blank">Our experts</a> </strong>will swiftly connect with a utility company that not only suits, but exceeds your requirements. The act of you searching for a suitable company comes to a stop as soon as you <strong><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/contact-us/" target="_blank">contact us</a>.</strong></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', 3, 0),
