(22, 'property management', 'property-management', '', '<div class="container">\r\n    <div class="row">\r\n        <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n            <div class="property-management-body">\r\n                <div class="custommenul">\r\n                    <div class="custommenul_item">\r\n                        <h2>Property Management</h2>\r\n                        <ul class="pmfirstprop">\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-analytic-reporting/">Analytic Reporting</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-collaboration/">Collaboration</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-document-management/">Document Management</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-free-trial/">Free Trial</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-move-in-move-out/">Move in, Move out</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-organize/">Organize</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-owner-portals/">Owner Portals</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-property-management-overview/">Property Management Overview</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-propertyware-mobile/">Propertyware Mobile</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-tenant-portals/">Tenant Portals</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-work-orders/">Work Orders</a></li>\r\n                        </ul>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="custommenul_item">\r\n                        <h2>Accounting</h2>\r\n                        <ul class="pmfirstacnt">\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-accounting-overview/">Accounting Overview</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-accounts-receivable/">Accounts Receivable</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-property-budgeting/">Property Budgeting</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-electronic-payments/">Electronic Payments</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-fee-management/">Fee Management</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-quickbooks-sync/">Quickbooks Sync</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-reconciliation/">Reconciliation</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/toronto-real-estate-reporting/">Reporting</a></li>\r\n                        </ul>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="custommenul_item">\r\n                        <h2>Contact Center</h2>\r\n                        <ul class="pmfirstcent">\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="#">Overview</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="#">Leasing Calls</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="#">Service Calls</a></li>\r\n                        </ul>\r\n                        <p class="pmmngmaint"><strong>Maintenance</strong></p>\r\n                        <ul class="pmfirstmaint">\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="#">Maintenance Overview</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="#">Inspections</a></li>\r\n                            <li><a class="content-interlink" href="#">Projects</a></li>\r\n                        </ul>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="clr"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                <p><strong>Property Management&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n                <p>At Homula, our property managers go above and beyond in order to ensure the daily operations of your real estate investment(s) are handled in a timely, professional and organized manner. From large investments to single property homes, you can count on both our financial and management skills.</p>\r\n                <p>Our responsibilities may vary based on the terms of our agreement, however, as our standard procedure, here is what we will always do for you:</p>\r\n                <p><strong>Rental Management: </strong>We connect you with top of the line Toronto real estate agents who have proven track records of success. These agents will only find tenants that have the qualities needed in order to rent out your unit. Our realtors will conduct face to face interviews and other screen techniques for the purpose of providing you with a tenant that is stable, honest, clean and reliable.</p>\r\n                <p><strong>Financial Management: </strong>We oversee and manage all of the financial transactions that are associated with your property. This includes obtaining the approval of expenses, transferring all net receipts to the owners on a month to month basis and collecting rent.</p>\r\n                <p><strong>Pre Delivery Inspection: </strong>We will effectively guide you through the entire resolution and inspection process. With our knowledge, you can rest assured that your investment remains secure.</p>\r\n                <p><strong>Tenant Screening: </strong>For your security, we pre-screen all potential tenants. Credit checks and employment letter are required and then verified by our expert team members. We make sure you are provided with the best tenant.</p>\r\n                <p><strong>Early Stage Engagement: </strong>In order to match newly constructed rental agreements and <a href="http://realestate.homula.com/realestate-search"><strong>MLS listings </strong></a>with the right tenant, we engage with developers at the early stages of construction.</p>\r\n                <p><strong>Financial Reporting: </strong>We will provide you with both annual and monthly financial statements. In addition to that, we will also assist you with the process of completing non-resident tax holding and submitting HST.</p>\r\n                <p><strong>Emergency Services: </strong>Our experts will always be readily available in order to provide solutions during an emergency for owners and tenants.</p>\r\n                <p><strong>Repairs and Maintenance: </strong>We have connected with well established contractors for the purpose of overseeing all maintenance and repairs that are needed for your unit. Your satisfaction is guaranteed.</p>\r\n                <p><strong>Regulatory, Legal and Financial Compliance: </strong>We accurately facilitate the resolution of every type of Tenant/Landlord manners, conduct property inspections and ensure tenant insurance compliance.</p>\r\n                <p><strong>Tenant Occupancy Assistance:&nbsp; </strong>As required, we coordinate the turnover of the unit with the board and condo management. We also facilitate inspections with new tenants prior to the occupying the unit.</p>\r\n                <h3>Connecting You With The Best Contractors</h3>\r\n                <p>At Homula, we have partnered with reputable contractors who are readily available to assist with any additional services/maintenance you may require. The contractors we are currently connecting with can further assist you with the following services:</p>\r\n                <ul>\r\n                    <li>Home renovation (for all areas)</li>\r\n                    <li>Moving</li>\r\n                    <li>Electrical repair and installation</li>\r\n                    <li>Painting, plastering and drywall repairs</li>\r\n                    <li>Plumbing repair and installation</li>\r\n                    <li>Cleaning services</li>\r\n                    <li>Carpet installation, repair and cleaning</li>\r\n                    <li>Tile re-grouting and installation</li>\r\n                    <li>Window cleaning, repair and installation</li>\r\n                    <li>General unit maintenance and repair</li>\r\n                    <li>Disaster restoration and water damage</li>\r\n                    <li>Uphoulstery cleaning, stain and odour removal</li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n                <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                <h3>Why&nbsp; Choose Us?</h3>\r\n                <p>Our experts are determined to not only meet, but exceed your every need. We make 10x the effort when compared to our competitors for the purpose of ensuring your investment is kept in a clean and secure state. We are client focused and results driven. Our experts provide the best and most reliable property management services. By working with us, you can expect:</p>\r\n                <ul>\r\n                    <li>Lower maintenance and repair costs</li>\r\n                    <li>Better tenant retention</li>\r\n                    <li>Fewer time consuming and costly legal issues</li>\r\n                    <li>A strict rent collection process</li>\r\n                    <li>An increase in property value</li>\r\n                    <li>Assistance with your taxes</li>\r\n                    <li>Less stress, and more freedom</li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n                <p>And more! </p>\r\n                <p><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/agents/" target="_blank">Our experts</a> are trained, certified and ready to assist you today!</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', 5, 0),
