fa fa-phone"></i> 647-999-8307</li>\r\n	                <li><i class="fa fa-at"></i> <a> graydonlogistics@yahoo.com</a>\r\n	                </li>\r\n	                <li><i class="fa fa-globe"></i> <a>www.graydonlogistics.org</a>\r\n	                </li>\r\n	                <li>ONTARIO</li>\r\n	            </ul>\r\n	        </div>\r\n	    </div>\r\n	    <div class="agent-row-content ">\r\n	        <h2 class="agent-row-title"><strong>Brighton Movers</strong></h2>\r\n	        <hr>\r\n	        <div class="agent-row-info">\r\n	            Gord Crawford\r\n	            <ul>\r\n	                <li><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> 647-404-7387</li>\r\n	                <li><i class="fa fa-at"></i>\r\n	                    <a> </a>\r\n	                </li>\r\n	                <li><i class="fa fa-globe"></i>\r\n	                    <a> </a>\r\n	                </li>\r\n	                <li>TORONTO</li>\r\n	            </ul>\r\n	        </div>\r\n	    </div>\r\n	    <div class="agent-row-content ">\r\n	        <h2 class="agent-row-title"><strong>AMJ Campbell</strong></h2>\r\n	        <hr>\r\n	        <div class="agent-row-info">\r\n	            Gary Kofoed\r\n	            <ul>\r\n	                <li><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> 416-891-2916</li>\r\n	                <li><i class="fa fa-at"></i> <a> gkofoed@amjcampbell.com</a>\r\n	                </li>\r\n	                <li><i class="fa fa-globe"></i> <a>www.amjcampbell.com</a>\r\n	                </li>\r\n	                <li>All Canada</li>\r\n	            </ul>\r\n	        </div>\r\n	    </div>\r\n	    <p><strong>Moving Company</strong>\r\n	    </p>\r\n	    <p>Homula connects you with the moving company you need to ensure that you, your family, and all of your belongs are transported carefully and professionally from your former home to your new one. After you’ve successfully made it through the Toronto real estate process, you want to be sure that this final piece of the moving process is completed safely and hassle-free. While the do-it-yourself option may have been an attractive solution in the past, there’s no reason not to hire a moving company to help you with this next move. Here are just a few reasons why a professional moving company is the best way to complete your transition into your new dream home.</p>\r\n	    <p><strong>Spend Time On More Important Matters</strong>\r\n	    </p>\r\n	    <p>Moving day can be one of the most stressful days in the year, especially if you’re trying to do it all yourself. Aside from actually transporting your belongings, you will need to have your telephone, cable, and utilities hooked up, change your identification, and unpack your belongings. When you’re not worried about lifting and transporting, you can spend moving day working on these equally as important tasks. This means that you won’t have to wait days for services to be hooked up, nor will you be living amongst boxes for weeks on end while you try and find the time to unpack. Simply have your movers take care of transportation, and you can spend that time doing more important matters.</p>\r\n	    <p><strong>Movers Are Incredibly Efficient</strong>\r\n	    </p>\r\n	    <p>Professional movers are just that, professionals. They have the tools, experience, and know-how to get an entire house moved in much less time than it would take an amateur to do it on their own. They can disassemble and reassemble your furniture, and will know just the right way to pack everything in the truck so your box of valuables doesn’t fall and break along the way.</p>\r\n	    <p><strong>Insurance and Liability Concerns<br>\r\n	</strong>\r\n	        <br> The only thing worse than asking your friends and family to help you move is seeing one of them become injured in the process. Professional movers are covered under workplace liability plans, meaning that even if an injury were to happen, you won’t find yourself liable for any damages. Most professional movers also have liability insurance, so even if something gets lost or damaged in the process, you can be sure that the costs of replacement will be covered.</p>\r\n	    <p><strong>Seasonal Moves</strong>\r\n	    </p>\r\n	    <p>Moving in extreme temperatures always carries with it increased risk for injury, not to mention contempt by your friends and family for being forced to help during frigid weather or blasting heat. Professional movers will be accustomed to these conditions, and will know how to approach the situation with the right gear and wearing the right clothing to get the job done.</p>\r\n	    <p><strong>You Might Actually Save Money</strong>\r\n	    </p>\r\n	    <p>While the upfront cost of hiring movers is obviously higher than asking friends and family to help for free, you might actually save yourself time in the long run. Renting a truck big enough to hold all your belongings can come at a huge cost, as can the price of gas, mileage, and insurance. There’s also the risk of multiple trips, which will drive up those costs even further. A professional moving company will be able to survey your home, and from there determine the best way to get everything moved in one trip. They are less likely to break something, and won’t demand food and refreshments when the job is done.</p>\r\n	    <p><strong>Contact Us</strong>\r\n	    </p>\r\n	    <p>Contact your real estate professionals at Homula to find the perfect moving company to handle your next move.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', '', '', 5, 0),
