(32, 'mortgage broker', 'mortgage-broker-professional-finder', '', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">At Homula, we pair you with the finest mortgage brokers in the industry! The </span>Toronto real estate <span style="font-weight: 400;">market prices are continuously increasing on a daily basis, as such, it is imperative for you to connect with a mortgage broker with the ability to get you a great deal. Whether your credit is bad, you have a low down payment, you are new to the country, or you have been recently divorced, our mortgage brokers can work to get you into the home of your dreams. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">By browsing through our exclusive </span>MLS listing <span style="font-weight: 400;">database, you will see a plethora of beautiful residential and commercial properties that our mortgage brokers will approve you for!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Mortgage payments are probably the biggest and most important bill anyone pays in their lifetime. This causes many people to enlist the services of a mortgage broker to find them the best terms and rates. A good broker can get you a good deal 99% of the time!</span>\r\n\r\n<h3>Advantages of Hiring a Mortgage Broker </h3>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Our experts can save you a lot of time and legwork. There are hundreds of lenders out there and finding the right one can be tiresome and stressful. Our brokers have contacts with a wide variety of lenders that are reliable and diligent. They also understand contracts and can steer you away from lenders who have hidden stipulations buried in their contracts. </span><a href="http://realestate.homula.com/agents/">Our experts </a><span style="font-weight: 400;">read between the lines and watch out for any hidden fees. At Homula, we have strong connections with a lot of lenders. Our brokers could even get you a special discount rate from a lender because he/she brings in so much business for that particular lending institution. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">The alternative to hiring one of our brokers is spending hours ploughing through dozens of lenders, looking for the right one. Our experts will save you both time and money. There are a lot of fees associated with getting a new mortgage, like application fees and appraisal fees. Our professionals might get a lender to waive some of the fees or get you a contract where the fees are much more favourable. Little things like that make a broker extremely helpful.</span>\r\n\r\n<h3>Choosing a Broker </h3>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Working with Homula is an excellent idea. Outside of Homula, some brokers are commission salesmen. Their main objective is to get you into a mortgage that gives them the highest compensation. You are looking at a contract with a low interest rate and similarly low fees. You are in it for the long haul, but the broker is thinking about short term profit. As a result, depending on the broker, you might not see eye to eye and you might not get the best deal. Also, mortgage brokers cannot provide estimates. A broker''s estimates may not be accurate and the lender may choose to change the terms on the final agreement. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">To summarize the pros and the cons, the best thing you can do is </span><a href="http://realestate.homula.com/contact-us/"><b>contact </b></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">a reputable mortgage broker today. </span>', '', '', 5, 0);
