(45, 'ask a question', 'ask-a-question', '', '<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-sm-12">\r\n<div class="askform">\r\n<form>\r\n<div style="display: none;"><input name="_wpcf7" type="hidden" value="1784" /> <input name="_wpcf7_version" type="hidden" value="4.5.1" /> <input name="_wpcf7_locale" type="hidden" value="en_US" /> <input name="_wpcf7_unit_tag" type="hidden" value="wpcf7-f1784-p1295-o1" /> <input name="_wpnonce" type="hidden" value="d30b27fc35" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-sm-8">\r\n<p class="cformfield"><label>Your Name (required)</label><span class="wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-name"><input aria-invalid="false" aria-required="true" class="wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-text wpcf7-validates-as-required" name="your-name" size="40" type="text" value="" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="cformfield"><label>Your Email (required)</label><span class="wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-email"><input aria-invalid="false" aria-required="true" class="wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-text wpcf7-email wpcf7-validates-as-required wpcf7-validates-as-email" name="your-email" size="40" type="email" value="" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="cformfield"><label>Category</label><span class="wpcf7-form-control-wrap menu-557"><select aria-invalid="false" class="wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-select" name="menu-557"><option value="Home Buying">Home Buying</option><option value="Rentals">Rentals</option><option value="Homula Questions">Homula Questions</option><option value="Using Homula">Using Homula</option><option value="Home Selling">Home Selling</option><option value="Mortgage">Mortgage</option><option value="Local Market">Local Market</option><option value="Utilities">Utilities</option><option value="Finding a professional">Finding a professional</option><option value="Tips for your home">Tips for your home</option><option value="Homula Tools">Homula Tools</option><option value="Bugs and Suggestions">Bugs and Suggestions</option></select></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-sm-4">\r\n<p class="cformfield">Your Question (required)<br />\r\n<span class="wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-question"><textarea aria-invalid="false" aria-required="true" class="wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-textarea wpcf7-validates-as-required" cols="40" name="your-question" rows="10" style="overflow: hidden; word-wrap: break-word; height: 96px;"></textarea></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><input class="wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-submit" type="submit" value="Submit" /><img alt="Sending ..." class="ajax-loader" src="http://realestate.homula.com/wp-content/plugins/contact-form-7/images/ajax-loader.gif" style="visibility: hidden;" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clr">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</form>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="ask_a_question_box">\r\n<p>We would love to hear from you! Whether you are a broker, investor, first time home buyer or a student, our Toronto real estate experts are readily available to answer any question(s) you may have about the real estate industry. At Homula, we pride ourselves in being available 24/7 for the purpose of ensuring you remain as knowledgeable as some of the biggest <b><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/agents/">real estate professionals</a></b> today! You may also ask us any questions about the MLS listing database.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is some advice from us to you!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3>Choosing the right area for you</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class="ask_a_question_box">\r\n<p>If you are new to the city or are just looking to relocate having a great agent again is a major plus. Taking some time and exploring neighbourhoods and educating yourself about the prices are very necessary. You need to make a smart purchase, knowing you are making a good investment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prices will vary throughout the city, so you should be shopping according to your budget. Even if you are not in the core of downtown there are lots of great/young up and coming neighborhoods that might work out well for you. Midtown or Uptown, North York also has growing neighborhoods that are getting makeovers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have a family and are looking for a home, there are so many options to choose from when looking for the perfect area for you. Think about if you will need schools nearby, transportation, shopping and etc. Budget again will be a major factor for you as well as what type of home you are looking for. <b>Homes for sale in Richmond Hill </b>are a great place to start looking, wonderful family communities, a lot to choose from and a great place to give you an idea of what might work or not work for you.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3>Option to Renovate</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class="ask_a_question_box">\r\n<p><a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/resale-homes/"><b>Buying a property </b></a>&nbsp;that is not exactly perfect but saving some money could also be a great deal for you. It has to be a smart purchase of course; you have to know what is worth renovating and what isn&rsquo;t. Definitely get an inspector and have someone with a professional eye on renovations there to help you. Have a set budget in mind allocated for your renovations (and always add extra here as renovations do tend to go over sometimes), figure out a plan of how you will complete them and when. Before moving in? After you are already living there?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also think about how long you are planning on living in the house, if you are settling down and are not looking to move in the near future at all then you could definitely do anything with the house just the way you like it. Customize it just for you! But if you are purchasing an investment property and are looking to sell in the next few years, I would definitely recommend really thinking about your choices. You want to make the house d&eacute;cor appealing to the majority, think clean lines, classic, nothing too overwhelming. <a class="content-interlink" href="http://realestate.homula.com/home-stagers/"><b>Hire a designer</b></a>. This will for sure pay off for you, most people don&rsquo;t realize why their house is not selling or they are not getting the price they want when it&rsquo;s something simple like blue walls in one room, purple in the other, tacky d&eacute;cor in the bathroom etc. All important things! Most people are looking for ready to move into/turnkey homes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b style="color: #337ab7;">Ask away! Homula is here to stay.</b></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n', '', '', 8, 0),
(46, 'help centre', 'help-centre', '', '<h2>BROWSE BY TOPIC</h2>\r\n<div class="help_centre_content">\r\n<h4>Get started</h4>\r\n<div class="help_centre_article">\r\n<span><i class="fa fa-database" aria-hidden="true"></i> 14 Articles</span><span>View All</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>You may be wondering by now, what are LTV and ATP ratios?</li>\r\n<li>What''s next?</li>\r\n<li>Budget</li>\r\n<li>The Big Decision</li>\r\n<li>Location, Location, Location.\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="help_centre_content">\r\n<h4>Get started</h4>\r\n<div class="help_centre_article">\r\n<span><i class="fa fa-database" aria-hidden="true"></i> 14 Articles</span><span>View All</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>You may be wondering by now, what are LTV and ATP ratios?</li>\r\n<li>What''s next?</li>\r\n<li>Budget</li>\r\n<li>The Big Decision</li>\r\n<li>Location, Location, Location.\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', '', '', 8, 0),
